A NEW ORAL STANDARD IN ANAEMIA OF CKD
EVRENZO can help your patients achieve and maintain their target Hb levels by providing a coordinated erythropietic response
EVRENZO sustained Hb levels without dose escalation, irrespective of inflammatory status
Patients treated with EVRENZO use less IV iron than those treated with ESA
Oral administration
means patients can avoid parenteral therapy
The convenience of treatment just 3 days a week
EVRENZO raises Hb levels without increasing CV risk compared to ESA in patients not on dialysis and those just
started on dialysis
The safety profile of EVRENZO has been evaluated in a clinical trial programme involving over 6,800 patients,
and was overall comparable to ESA for the majority of safety variables
